Land PR #48 (Kozynets/Fröse, arXiv:2306.15263) on top of v2: 2D angular-cascade extension via block-stitched ETD2RK, with the muon multiple-scattering damping folded into the diagonal D and config.enable_2D auto-detection. Validated against PR baseline; ~24x faster at unchanged accuracy. See docs/mceq_v1.x_v2_diff.md section 11.
